reviewText: Not at all what I expeced.

GREAT WORKOUT!  THIS WAS MADE A WHILE AGO, BUT A GREAT WORK OUT PROGRAM IS NEVER OUTDATED!
HAVE BEEN DOING AT HOME AND IN THE GYM!

I really like Regis' workout video (after all these years).  It is not difficult, easy to follow.  I jump rope and do a little aerobics while he is talking at the beginning and during the portions with Joy, Kathy Lee and the producer. ..then fall right into his workout.  He makes it fun. I wish it came in DVD format.
